Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:51.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs30\frz15.145\c&HE2DCD2&\pos(310,228)}想要下雨的时候一起撑伞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:51.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs30\c&HADD0B2&\pos(606,268)}你喜欢我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:51.30,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\fs30\frz342.705\c&HC0AFD7&\pos(982,88)}一起手牵手去购物！
